{"tid":1404392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］今日邊撚個再話入TVB就係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:00:11.000Z","uid":209198,"like":698,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"bab6e91ccd9c23082f17a2a98343d9a22fc8ed63","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"講咗好撚多次<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚入TVB</span></strong></span><br />\n係將軍澳住咗咁撚多年<br />\n老老柒柒 講比你班撚屌知老西咁多次<br />\n叫撚曬你地咪鳩入TVB個位<br />\n一入走唔到等仆街奶袋底<br />\n點知今日一望都仲係有人吹風話要入TVB<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我T你老母臭化西</span></span></strong><br />\n本人在此宣布<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>除非前線即場決定 否則再鳩帶風向話入TVB者 我立刻馬上第一個同你割席 所有因進入TVB範圍而被拘捕義士全部係你責任</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"88accc99faf270673125687105805d8f3384df89","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"51c09b7869adcf3f803e0e5c4306d456510cc73e","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"同我推<br />\n除非前線開聲<br />\n否則我屌柒所有話入TVB既人老母"},{"pid":"264ab306b63190208ef7f38928f8ba0f180261a5","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1639576ea6975dad89ca8ce21c3297dbfcd8a764","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀你班撚樣"},{"pid":"91994a671d8e5fb30015de9bf1eb3b1225ba2c25","tid":1404392,"uid":209198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2866d0e9772bd126a74e09154c05ff09d0f86ef1","tid":1404392,"uid":254022,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"同埋唔好行過去環保大道"},{"pid":"2f867fac2175ec59597f